 <instruction>Thue das In ain <tool en="container" commodity="Q987767">haefelein</tool></instruction>
 vnd <instruction>ruer es schon ab das es wol</instruction>
 <instruction>das du hast gehackt klain das thue In den <ingredient en="deer blood" commodity="Q5250691">schwaiss</ingredient></instruction>
 vnd <instruction>ain rain <ingredient en="lard" commodity="Q72827">schmalcz</ingredient> thue darunder</instruction>
 vnd <instruction>lass sieden darInne</instruction>
 <instruction>machs ab das es starck sej</instruction>
 vnd <instruction>ein guot <ingredient en="spice" commodity="Q42527">gewuercz</ingredient> saee darauf das sey von <ingredient en="ginger" commodity="Q15046077">ymber</ingredient> <ingredient en="clove" commodity="Q15622897">naegelein</ingredient> <ingredient en="unrefined cane sugar" commodity="Q57656231">zucker</ingredient> vnd <ingredient en="cinnamon" commodity="Q28165">zymen</ingredient></instruction>
 <instruction>Er sol es damit bestraeen</instruction>
